### /handleLogin

This endpoint is used to handle the login process.

#### Request

- Method: POST

- URL: `http://localhost:3001/handleLogin`

- Body (x-www-form-urlencoded):

    - `UID` (text)

    - `fullName` (text)

    - `email` (text)

    - `photoUrl` (text)


#### Response

The response of this request can be documented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "msg": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "UID": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "apiKey": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

